{"word":"G5578 - ψευδοπροφήτης - pseudoprophḗtēs - psyoo-dop-rof-ay'-tace - False prophet","slug":"G5578","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψευδοπροφήτης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pseudoprophḗtēs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>psyoo-dop-rof-ay'-tace"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>False prophet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C8;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C6;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03C2; - pseudoprophe&#x0304;te&#x0304;s</b> - <i>psyoo-dop-rof-ay'-tace</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5571\">G5571</a> and <a href=\"#/G4396\">G4396</a>; a <i>spurious prophet</i>, that is, <i>pretended foreteller</i> or religious <i>impostor:</i> - false prophet."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5571\">G5571</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572\">G5572</a>, <a href=\"#/G5573\">G5573</a>, <a href=\"#/G5574\">G5574</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>, <a href=\"#/G5579\">G5579</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580\">G5580</a>, <a href=\"#/G5581\">G5581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5582\">G5582</a>, <a href=\"#/G5583\">G5583</a>, <a href=\"#/G893\">G893</a>"}]}